## Stack Tecnologico

| Componente | Version |
|------------|---------|
| Python | 3.12+ |
| FastAPI | 0.115+ |
| SQLAlchemy | 2.0+ (async) |
| Pydantic | 2.10+ |
| uv | latest |
| pytest | 8.3+ |

## Prerequisitos

- Python >= 3.12
- uv (package manager)
- Docker + Docker Compose
- PostgreSQL 15+ (local o via Docker)

## Inicio Rapido

```bash
# 1. Instalar dependencias
uv sync

# 2. Copiar variables de entorno
cp .env.sample .env

# 3. Levantar infraestructura local
docker compose up -d

# 4. Ejecutar en modo desarrollo
uv run uvicorn src.main:app --reload --port {{ app_port }}
```

