| POST | `{{ context_path }}/api/v1/{{ module.resource_path_resolved }}` | Crear {{ module.entity_name }} |
| GET | `{{ context_path }}/api/v1/{{ module.resource_path_resolved }}/{id}` | Obtener {{ module.entity_name }} |
| PUT | `{{ context_path }}/api/v1/{{ module.resource_path_resolved }}/{id}` | Actualizar {{ module.entity_name }} |
| DELETE | `{{ context_path }}/api/v1/{{ module.resource_path_resolved }}/{id}` | Eliminar {{ module.entity_name }} |
{% endfor %}

## Comandos

| Comando | Descripcion |
|---------|-------------|
| `uv run uvicorn src.main:app --reload` | Desarrollo con hot-reload |
| `uv run pytest` | Ejecutar tests |
| `uv run pytest --cov` | Tests con coverage |
| `uv run ruff check src/` | Lint |
| `uv run ruff format src/` | Format |
| `uv run mypy src/` | Type check |

## Arquitectura

```
src/
├── main.py             ← App factory FastAPI
├── config/             ← Settings, DB, logging, security
├── commons/            ← ApiResponse, Pagination, AuditMixin
├── middleware/         ← Correlation-ID, error handler, security headers
├── errors/             ← BolivarBusinessError, ErrorType
├── utils/              ← Sanitizacion, utilidades fecha
{% for module in modules %}
└── {{ module.module_name }}/           ← Dominio {{ module.entity_name }}
    ├── router.py
    ├── service.py
    ├── repository.py
    ├── models.py
    ├── schemas/
    └── tests/
{% endfor %}
```

